               <msContents>
                  <summary>The Book of Ezekiel, Text and Commentary (Amharic), ትርጓሜ፡ ሕዝቅኤል፡, Biography of Ezekiel, ዜና፡ (ሕዝቅኤል፡), Entry about Ezekiel from the Synaxarium, እመጽሐፈ፡ ስንክሳር፡, List of the canon of the Scriptures, ኁልቈ፡ መጻሕፍት፡, commissioned by Nǝburä ‘Ǝdǝ Dǝmeṭǝros Gäbrä Maryam</summary>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="289v" facs="005">pp. 1-578</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5975CommEzekiel">Amharic
                                                  Commentary on Ezekiel</title>
                    <note>There are scribal errors in numbering the pages, so p.275 is written on two consecutive pages, and p. 543 is followed by p. 534. Page numbers here are those written on the page</note>
                    <textLang mainLang="am" otherLangs="gez">Amharic and Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="4v" facs="005">pp. 1-8</locus>
                    <title>Commentary on the Introduction to Ezekiel</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="am" otherLangs="gez">Amharic and Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                    <incipit>
                      <foreign xml:lang="gez">መቅድም፡ ዘሕዝቅኤል፡ ነቢይ፡ </foreign>
                      <foreign xml:lang="am">ሕዝቅኤል፡ ማለት፡ </foreign>
                      <foreign xml:lang="gez">ፅኑዕ፡ ፅንዐ፡ አምላክ፡ </foreign>
                      <foreign xml:lang="am">ማለት ነው። ሕዝቅያስ ማለት፡ </foreign>
                      <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዕኑዕ፡ ጽንዐ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ </foreign>
                      <foreign xml:lang="am">ማለት፡ እንደ፡ ሆነ፡ ነገዱ፡ ከሌዊ፡ ትውልዱ፡ ከአሮን፡ ነው። አባቱ፡ ቡዝ ይባላል፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></foreign>
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                    <locus from="5r" to="288v" facs="009">pp.9-564</locus>
                    <title>Commentary on Ezekiel, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ትርጓሜ፡ ሕዝቅኤል፡</foreign></title>
                    <textLang mainLang="am" otherLangs="gez">Amharic and Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                    <incipit>
                      <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወኮነ፡ በ፴ ዓመት፡ በራብዕ፡ ወርኅ፡ አመ፡ ሐሙሱ፡ </foreign>
                      <foreign xml:lang="am">ስለምን፡ በዋዌ፡ ጀመረ፡ ቢሉ፡ ከእርሱ፡ አስቀድሞ፡ ብዙ፡ ነቢያት፡ ተነሥተው፡ ብዙ፡ መጻሕፍት፡ ተጽፈው፡ ነበርና፡ ነገሩን፡ ከነዚያ፡
                        ለማያያዝ፡ ከቀደመውም፡ ማያያዝ፡ የነቢያት፡ ልማድ፡ ነው። <gap reason="omitted"/></foreign>
                      </incipit>
                    </msItem>

                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                    <locus from="288v" to="289r" facs="293">pp. 565-566</locus>
                    <title>Sections of the Inherited land and the Names of the Twelve Tribes of Israel (Ezekiel 40–48), <foreign xml:lang="gez">ክፍለ፡ ምድረ፡ ርስት፡ ወአስማቲሆሙ፡ ለአሠርቱ፡ ወክልኤቱ፡ አንጋደ፡ እስራኤል፡</foreign></title>
                      <textLang mainLang="am" otherLangs="gez">Amharic and Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                    </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                    <locus from="289r" to="290r" facs="293">pp. 566-568</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4334Ezek">Life of Ezekiel<foreign xml:lang="gez">ዜና፡ (ሕዝቅኤል፡)</foreign></title>
                    <textLang mainLang="am" otherLangs="gez">Amharic and Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                    <incipit>
                      <foreign xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አዶናይ፡ ከመ፡ ዘይሰቲ፡ ነጥበ፡ ማይ፡ እምቀላይ፡ ባሕር፡ ዐቢይ፡ ንጽሕፍ፡ ኅዳጠ፡ እምዜናሁ፡ ለሕዝቅኤል፡ ነቢይ፡ ወልደ፡ ቡዝ፡ ካህን፡ ዘእምደቂቀ፡ ሳዶቅ። ተብህለ፡ በእንቲአሁ፡ ከመ፡ ውእቱ፡ ረድአ፡
                        ኤርምያስ፡ ነቢይ፡ እምንዕሱ፡ ይቤ፡ ዮናታን፡ መተርጉም፡ በውስተ፡ መጽሐፉ፤ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                      </foreign>
                      </incipit>
                      <note>Noted as found in Hebrew</note>

                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                    <locus from="290r" to="290v" facs="294">pp. 568-569</locus>
                    <title type="incomplete">Entry from the Synaxarium about Ezekiel</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">እመጽሐፈ፡ ስንክሳር፡ አመ፡ ፭ ለሚያዝያ፡ አዕረፈ፡ ሕዝቅኤል፡ ዐቢይ፡ ነቢይ፡ ወልደ፡ ቡዝ፡ ካህን፡ ዝንቱ፡ ነቢይ፡ ተፄወወ፡ ኀበ፡ ሀገረ፡ ባቢሎን፡ ሶበ፡ ፄወዎሙ፡ ናቡከደነፆር፡ ንጉሥ፡ ለደቂቀ፡ እስራኤል፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                    <locus from="290v" to="293r" facs="295">pp. 569-574</locus>
                    <title>Image of Ezekiel, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መልክዓ፡ ሕዝቅኤል፡</foreign></title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">በቀዳሚ፡ ገብረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ሰማየ፡ ወምድረ።
                    ወመልዕልተ፡ ሰማይ፡ ውዱድ፡ አስተዳለወ፡ መንበረ።
                    ዘንተኒ፡ ሕዝቅኤል፡ በአዕይንቲሁ፡ ነጸረ።
                    እስመ፡ ቦአ፡ ለተልዕኮ፡ ወለተመጠወ፡ ምሥጢረ።
                    ቅድስተ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ ኪሩቤል፡ ዘኮኑ፡ መፆረ።</incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                    <locus from="293r" to="295r" facs="297">pp. 574-578</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4982ListCan">List of canonical
                                                  books</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="am" otherLangs="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                    <incipit xml:lang="am">አይሁድ፡ የብሉይ፡ ኪዳን፡ መጻሕፍት፡ ፳፬ ይሏቸዋል። ፳፬ቱን፡ ደግሞ፡ ባራቱ፡ ክፍለ፡ ዘመን፡ አምሳል፡ እንደ፡ ወንጌል፡ ካራት፡ ይከፍሏቸዋል፡ ቍጥራቸውና፡ ክፍላቸውም፡ እንዲህ፡ ነው። <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>

                    <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                    <locus target="#295r" facs="299">Fol. 295r</locus>
                        <q>This book was begun on the fourth of Säne and finished on the thirtieth of Yäkkatit.
                        This book of the prophet Ezekiel in Gǝʿǝz and Amharic was commissioned by Nǝburä ‘Ǝdǝ Dǝmeṭǝros Gäbrä Maryam,
                        whose baptismal name is Kinä Śǝlasie, and the name of his mother is Wälätä Ab. It is written in 1949 EC (=1956/57)</q>
                        <note>mentioning the commissioning by <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3504Demetros"> Dǝmeṭros Gäbrä Maryam </persName>, on <date when-custom="130649" calendar="ethiopian">የካቲት ፲፫, ፲፻፵፱፡</date></note>
                    </colophon>


                </msItem>

               </msContents>
